# AI Team Delivery Workflow

- Use `meeting-explorer` or `ai-team-orchestrator` before large changes.
- Define acceptance criteria before implementation when requirements are vague.
- Keep work in small, reviewable slices.
- Prefer feature branches and pull requests over direct changes to `main`.
- Run QA reasoning before claiming merge readiness.
- Call out blockers, assumptions, and missing GitHub information explicitly.
